overview: Video Gag (pronounced vee-day-oh gag) is a French television series that airs weekly on French broadcast channel TF1. It is essentially a French version of "America's Funniest Home Videos" or the British "You've been framed!" and uses hilarious videos sent in by viewers. Although the videos are primarily French in origin, it also uses other videos from other countries on occasion.
